{{ 'aaw-customer-voices.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}

<section class="aaw-voices aaw-voices--{{ section.settings.layout_mode }}" aria-labelledby="aaw-voices-title-{{ section.id }}">
  <div class="aaw-voices__wrap">
    <div class="aaw-voices__head">
      <div>
        <p class="aaw-voices__kicker">{{ section.settings.eyebrow }}</p>
        <h2 id="aaw-voices-title-{{ section.id }}">{{ section.settings.heading }}</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="aaw-voices__intro">
        <p>{{ section.settings.intro }}</p>
        {% if section.settings.layout_mode == 'home' %}
          <a class="aaw-voices__link" href="{{ section.settings.page_link }}">Read more customer voices</a>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    </div>

    {% if section.settings.layout_mode == 'page' %}
      <div class="aaw-voices__hero">
        <figure>
          <img src="{{ 'aaw-ins-gallery-custom-2025.webp' | asset_url }}" alt="AAW custom in-ear monitor shell craft and finishing" width="900" height="900" loading="eager">
        </figure>
        <div>
          <span>Customer voices</span>
          <h3>Real owner impressions from AAW listeners around the world.</h3>
          <p>Collected through AAW dealers via Judge.me, these comments focus on fit, sound, comfort, and everyday listening.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    {% endif %}

    <div class="aaw-voices__grid">
      <article class="aaw-voice-card is-featured" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Review"><span itemprop="itemReviewed" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Product"><meta itemprop="name" content="AAW in-ear monitors"></span>
        <div class="aaw-voice-card__meta" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Rating"><meta itemprop="worstRating" content="1"><meta itemprop="bestRating" content="5"><meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5"><b>5 / 5</b></div>
        <blockquote itemprop="reviewBody">I was very pleasantly surprised just how good AAW monitors are. The overall sound is quite balanced, they do have very detailed bass, sub bass and treble, but the mids are not so recessed as would be the case with more typical V shaped sounding IEM&#x27;s.</blockquote>
        <footer itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name">Steve S.</span></footer>
      </article>

      <article class="aaw-voice-card" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Review"><span itemprop="itemReviewed" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Product"><meta itemprop="name" content="AAW in-ear monitors"></span>
        <div class="aaw-voice-card__meta" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Rating"><meta itemprop="worstRating" content="1"><meta itemprop="bestRating" content="5"><meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5"><b>5 / 5</b></div>
        <blockquote itemprop="reviewBody">Excellent product. This is my first CIEM and I can say I am very much impressed. It fits perfectly snugged in my ears. I thought it sounded just the same when using tunes on my phone, but when I plugged it in the monitors, I can hear clearly the distinct sounds. The vocals and the bass is clear and crisp.</blockquote>
        <footer itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name">AJ L.</span></footer>
      </article>

      <article class="aaw-voice-card" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Review"><span itemprop="itemReviewed" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Product"><meta itemprop="name" content="AAW in-ear monitors"></span>
        <div class="aaw-voice-card__meta" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Rating"><meta itemprop="worstRating" content="1"><meta itemprop="bestRating" content="5"><meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5"><b>5 / 5</b></div>
        <blockquote itemprop="reviewBody">Great fit, great isolation, great material and good sound for the price. Sound wise is big and quite wide. Bass is satisfying and mids are ok just that the treble is very recessed but its what makes it non-fatiguing for long term listening. Overall an enjoyable iem.</blockquote>
        <footer itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name">Elias T.</span></footer>
      </article>

      <article class="aaw-voice-card" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Review"><span itemprop="itemReviewed" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Product"><meta itemprop="name" content="AAW in-ear monitors"></span>
        <div class="aaw-voice-card__meta" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Rating"><meta itemprop="worstRating" content="1"><meta itemprop="bestRating" content="5"><meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5"><b>5 / 5</b></div>
        <blockquote itemprop="reviewBody">This is my first time buy a CIEM, and they totally nailed it. Their ear impression quality is great, constantly checking on my comfort levels, worked out everything so professionally.</blockquote>
        <footer itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name">Seah H.</span></footer>
      </article>

      <article class="aaw-voice-card" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Review"><span itemprop="itemReviewed" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Product"><meta itemprop="name" content="AAW in-ear monitors"></span>
        <div class="aaw-voice-card__meta" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Rating"><meta itemprop="worstRating" content="1"><meta itemprop="bestRating" content="5"><meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5"><b>5 / 5</b></div>
        <blockquote itemprop="reviewBody">Pros: very nice sound. clear high freqs, detailed. subdued bass, but still clear and detailed. Cons: A little bit heavy, so have to carefully choose ear tips for good fit (I have to make custom ear tips). No so good noise isolation.</blockquote>
        <footer itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name">Artem</span></footer>
      </article>

      <article class="aaw-voice-card" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Review"><span itemprop="itemReviewed" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Product"><meta itemprop="name" content="AAW in-ear monitors"></span>
        <div class="aaw-voice-card__meta" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Rating"><meta itemprop="worstRating" content="1"><meta itemprop="bestRating" content="5"><meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5"><b>5 / 5</b></div>
        <blockquote itemprop="reviewBody">Really excited as it is my first set of CIEMs! The whole process was fuss free and I&#x27;ve got to say, they have an excellent customer support service going on. They replied to my queries with great detail within 24 hours. Even though I haven&#x27;t gotten my pair, the demos sounded awesome.</blockquote>
        <footer itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name">Jia T.</span></footer>
      </article>

      <article class="aaw-voice-card" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Review"><span itemprop="itemReviewed" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Product"><meta itemprop="name" content="AAW in-ear monitors"></span>
        <div class="aaw-voice-card__meta" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Rating"><meta itemprop="worstRating" content="1"><meta itemprop="bestRating" content="5"><meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5"><b>5 / 5</b></div>
        <blockquote itemprop="reviewBody">I just got my AAW monitors, and it was really amazing. The most impressive thing is the highs, the ceremic twetter really sounds like the electrostatic driver, and gives a very crysp highs with no irritating peaks. The mid and bass are also well balanced.</blockquote>
        <footer itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name">k n.</span></footer>
      </article>

      <article class="aaw-voice-card" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Review"><span itemprop="itemReviewed" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Product"><meta itemprop="name" content="AAW in-ear monitors"></span>
        <div class="aaw-voice-card__meta" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Rating"><meta itemprop="worstRating" content="1"><meta itemprop="bestRating" content="5"><meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5"><b>5 / 5</b></div>
        <blockquote itemprop="reviewBody">I had AAW monitors before this and thought it sounded better than some CIEMs above the price range. Now, it has the same clarity but a more pronounced bass. That makes it alot more natural.</blockquote>
        <footer itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name">Manfred K.</span></footer>
      </article>

      {% if section.settings.layout_mode == 'page' %}

      <article class="aaw-voice-card" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Review"><span itemprop="itemReviewed" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Product"><meta itemprop="name" content="AAW in-ear monitors"></span>
        <div class="aaw-voice-card__meta" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Rating"><meta itemprop="worstRating" content="1"><meta itemprop="bestRating" content="5"><meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5"><b>5 / 5</b></div>
        <blockquote itemprop="reviewBody">The sound quality is great. Bass is better than my expectation. For this price range, I would said this is the highest C/P value cm ear monitor.</blockquote>
        <footer itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name">Tsz L.</span></footer>
      </article>

      <article class="aaw-voice-card" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Review"><span itemprop="itemReviewed" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Product"><meta itemprop="name" content="AAW in-ear monitors"></span>
        <div class="aaw-voice-card__meta" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Rating"><meta itemprop="worstRating" content="1"><meta itemprop="bestRating" content="5"><meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5"><b>5 / 5</b></div>
        <blockquote itemprop="reviewBody">Bass is powerful and fun. Mid and treble are very natural. Furthermore, the shell is superior quality, so it’s great value for money!</blockquote>
        <footer itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name">T.M.</span></footer>
      </article>

      <article class="aaw-voice-card" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Review"><span itemprop="itemReviewed" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Product"><meta itemprop="name" content="AAW in-ear monitors"></span>
        <div class="aaw-voice-card__meta" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Rating"><meta itemprop="worstRating" content="1"><meta itemprop="bestRating" content="5"><meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5"><b>5 / 5</b></div>
        <blockquote itemprop="reviewBody">Got it within the time. The sound quality was great and clear. The ear phone also fit perfectly into my ear and it then final product was great! Love it a lot!</blockquote>
        <footer itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name">Yong R.</span></footer>
      </article>

      <article class="aaw-voice-card" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Review"><span itemprop="itemReviewed" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Product"><meta itemprop="name" content="AAW in-ear monitors"></span>
        <div class="aaw-voice-card__meta" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Rating"><meta itemprop="worstRating" content="1"><meta itemprop="bestRating" content="5"><meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5"><b>5 / 5</b></div>
        <blockquote itemprop="reviewBody">The sound quality of these IEM’s is awesome and the sound stage is very good. Positional audio in games is accurate and the microphone quality is excellent.</blockquote>
        <footer itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name">DColeman</span></footer>
      </article>

      <article class="aaw-voice-card" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Review"><span itemprop="itemReviewed" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Product"><meta itemprop="name" content="AAW in-ear monitors"></span>
        <div class="aaw-voice-card__meta" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Rating"><meta itemprop="worstRating" content="1"><meta itemprop="bestRating" content="5"><meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5"><b>5 / 5</b></div>
        <blockquote itemprop="reviewBody">Product is as described by title; the sound signature is fun, natural and engaging yet the different frequencies were impressively well balanced. Went for the advance service and ended up receiving my product 5 working days after I&#x27;ve placed the order.</blockquote>
        <footer itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name">Tianchang L.</span></footer>
      </article>

      <article class="aaw-voice-card" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Review"><span itemprop="itemReviewed" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Product"><meta itemprop="name" content="AAW in-ear monitors"></span>
        <div class="aaw-voice-card__meta" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Rating"><meta itemprop="worstRating" content="1"><meta itemprop="bestRating" content="5"><meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="4"><b>4 / 5</b></div>
        <blockquote itemprop="reviewBody">It&#x27;s not easy to find in-ears which fits well and a has good isolation and a good or natural sound. I think AAW monitors has all. The sound [double bass-vocals-violins-percussionis and acoustics] is close to the sound I always hear in a concert hall. For me the sound and the fit is better than focal sphear or rha t20.</blockquote>
        <footer itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name">Piet B.</span></footer>
      </article>

      <article class="aaw-voice-card" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Review"><span itemprop="itemReviewed" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Product"><meta itemprop="name" content="AAW in-ear monitors"></span>
        <div class="aaw-voice-card__meta" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Rating"><meta itemprop="worstRating" content="1"><meta itemprop="bestRating" content="5"><meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5"><b>5 / 5</b></div>
        <blockquote itemprop="reviewBody">It is great value for money! I really like this product, so I hope that with CIEM version will be released too.</blockquote>
        <footer itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name">T.M.</span></footer>
      </article>

      <article class="aaw-voice-card" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Review"><span itemprop="itemReviewed" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Product"><meta itemprop="name" content="AAW in-ear monitors"></span>
        <div class="aaw-voice-card__meta" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Rating"><meta itemprop="worstRating" content="1"><meta itemprop="bestRating" content="5"><meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5"><b>5 / 5</b></div>
        <blockquote itemprop="reviewBody">The process went smoothly and the monitors were delivered in about 5 weeks. The fit&#x27;s good and the sound is great. The in-flight adapter had a short which distorted speech on movies. the dealer replaced it immediately (and gave me an extra spare) Overall I&#x27;m very happy with the product and the service.</blockquote>
        <footer itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name">Anthony F.</span></footer>
      </article>

      <article class="aaw-voice-card" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Review"><span itemprop="itemReviewed" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Product"><meta itemprop="name" content="AAW in-ear monitors"></span>
        <div class="aaw-voice-card__meta" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Rating"><meta itemprop="worstRating" content="1"><meta itemprop="bestRating" content="5"><meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5"><b>5 / 5</b></div>
        <blockquote itemprop="reviewBody">IEM was well fitted, didnt need to do a refit. Sound was the same as what i had tested at their office :Excellent Will definitely come back to the dealer if there&#x27;s a need to. Keep up the good work!</blockquote>
        <footer itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name">Junkang W.</span></footer>
      </article>

      <article class="aaw-voice-card" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Review"><span itemprop="itemReviewed" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Product"><meta itemprop="name" content="AAW in-ear monitors"></span>
        <div class="aaw-voice-card__meta" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Rating"><meta itemprop="worstRating" content="1"><meta itemprop="bestRating" content="5"><meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5"><b>5 / 5</b></div>
        <blockquote itemprop="reviewBody">These in ears are just so amazing!! Perfect fit and in my opinion almost perfect sound (i&#x27;d like to have a bit more high end ) I really recommend these!!!</blockquote>
        <footer itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name">L.Standop</span></footer>
      </article>

      <article class="aaw-voice-card" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Review"><span itemprop="itemReviewed" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Product"><meta itemprop="name" content="AAW in-ear monitors"></span>
        <div class="aaw-voice-card__meta" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Rating"><meta itemprop="worstRating" content="1"><meta itemprop="bestRating" content="5"><meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5"><b>5 / 5</b></div>
        <blockquote itemprop="reviewBody">They are relatively wide in soundstage and easy on songs. Unbeatable price:performance and a good first step if you&#x27;re looking towards getting customs</blockquote>
        <footer itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name">Yong T.</span></footer>
      </article>

      <article class="aaw-voice-card" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Review"><span itemprop="itemReviewed" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Product"><meta itemprop="name" content="AAW in-ear monitors"></span>
        <div class="aaw-voice-card__meta" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Rating"><meta itemprop="worstRating" content="1"><meta itemprop="bestRating" content="5"><meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5"><b>5 / 5</b></div>
        <blockquote itemprop="reviewBody">The sound is closer to the bass. The ear fits well and doesn&#x27;t come off easily when combined with the cable wires. Can be worn for a long time.</blockquote>
        <footer itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name">りょう</span></footer>
      </article>

      <article class="aaw-voice-card" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Review"><span itemprop="itemReviewed" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Product"><meta itemprop="name" content="AAW in-ear monitors"></span>
        <div class="aaw-voice-card__meta" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Rating"><meta itemprop="worstRating" content="1"><meta itemprop="bestRating" content="5"><meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5"><b>5 / 5</b></div>
        <blockquote itemprop="reviewBody">Once you put it on, the rest of the world just went silent. The first time I used it was on Disturbed - Sound of Silence. The vocals were clear and strong, with the instruments complementing nicely in the background. Definitely a great driver.</blockquote>
        <footer itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name">Yeok q.</span></footer>
      </article>

      <article class="aaw-voice-card" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Review"><span itemprop="itemReviewed" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Product"><meta itemprop="name" content="AAW in-ear monitors"></span>
        <div class="aaw-voice-card__meta" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Rating"><meta itemprop="worstRating" content="1"><meta itemprop="bestRating" content="5"><meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5"><b>5 / 5</b></div>
        <blockquote itemprop="reviewBody">These IEM are great! In terms of sound they really were what I was looking for. One thing tho, the cable does get a little sticky in humid weather, would be great if there was a solution or replacement!</blockquote>
        <footer itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name">Michael C.</span></footer>
      </article>

      <article class="aaw-voice-card" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Review"><span itemprop="itemReviewed" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Product"><meta itemprop="name" content="AAW in-ear monitors"></span>
        <div class="aaw-voice-card__meta" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Rating"><meta itemprop="worstRating" content="1"><meta itemprop="bestRating" content="5"><meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5"><b>5 / 5</b></div>
        <blockquote itemprop="reviewBody">The IEM is of high quality and excellent for gaming. However, the cable is a bit short and if you are using an amp, you would need a silencer. Other than these points, I am very happy with my purchase.</blockquote>
        <footer itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name">immi B.</span></footer>
      </article>

      <article class="aaw-voice-card" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Review"><span itemprop="itemReviewed" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Product"><meta itemprop="name" content="AAW in-ear monitors"></span>
        <div class="aaw-voice-card__meta" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Rating"><meta itemprop="worstRating" content="1"><meta itemprop="bestRating" content="5"><meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5"><b>5 / 5</b></div>
        <blockquote itemprop="reviewBody">The best in-ears for the price as compared to other universals such as the se215. AAW monitors are a great set of customs for new owners to start their venture into the CIEM world.</blockquote>
        <footer itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name">Masagos M.</span></footer>
      </article>

      <article class="aaw-voice-card" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Review"><span itemprop="itemReviewed" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Product"><meta itemprop="name" content="AAW in-ear monitors"></span>
        <div class="aaw-voice-card__meta" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Rating"><meta itemprop="worstRating" content="1"><meta itemprop="bestRating" content="5"><meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5"><b>5 / 5</b></div>
        <blockquote itemprop="reviewBody">Extremely satisfied with the purchase. Packaging itself could be better as the AAW box needed extra effort to remove from the cardboard box. But that’s just the box. AAW monitors itself sounds incredible. The workmanship was excellent and the lead time was much shorter than advertised.</blockquote>
        <footer itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name">Mohd N.</span></footer>
      </article>

      <article class="aaw-voice-card" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Review"><span itemprop="itemReviewed" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Product"><meta itemprop="name" content="AAW in-ear monitors"></span>
        <div class="aaw-voice-card__meta" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Rating"><meta itemprop="worstRating" content="1"><meta itemprop="bestRating" content="5"><meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5"><b>5 / 5</b></div>
        <blockquote itemprop="reviewBody">Took about 8 weeks for mine to be received; sounds great and fits great, didn&#x27;t need to go for a refit. Definitely value for money!</blockquote>
        <footer itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name">Isaac W.</span></footer>
      </article>

      <article class="aaw-voice-card" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Review"><span itemprop="itemReviewed" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Product"><meta itemprop="name" content="AAW in-ear monitors"></span>
        <div class="aaw-voice-card__meta" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Rating"><meta itemprop="worstRating" content="1"><meta itemprop="bestRating" content="5"><meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5"><b>5 / 5</b></div>
        <blockquote itemprop="reviewBody">The ear impression fitted perfectly and I am very satisfied. Effects were per I experienced with the samples at the store.</blockquote>
        <footer itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name">Ng E.</span></footer>
      </article>

      <article class="aaw-voice-card" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Review"><span itemprop="itemReviewed" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Product"><meta itemprop="name" content="AAW in-ear monitors"></span>
        <div class="aaw-voice-card__meta" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Rating"><meta itemprop="worstRating" content="1"><meta itemprop="bestRating" content="5"><meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5"><b>5 / 5</b></div>
        <blockquote itemprop="reviewBody">Great choice if you want an open sounding &amp; balanced IEM. Can&#x27;t really go wrong with any of the dealer&#x27;s products!</blockquote>
        <footer itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name">Phong N.</span></footer>
      </article>

      <article class="aaw-voice-card" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Review"><span itemprop="itemReviewed" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Product"><meta itemprop="name" content="AAW in-ear monitors"></span>
        <div class="aaw-voice-card__meta" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Rating"><meta itemprop="worstRating" content="1"><meta itemprop="bestRating" content="5"><meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5"><b>5 / 5</b></div>
        <blockquote itemprop="reviewBody">I have always been a dynamic driver IEM lover and this is truly amazing! The resolution rivals multi BA setup.</blockquote>
        <footer itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name">Laz</span></footer>
      </article>

      <article class="aaw-voice-card" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Review"><span itemprop="itemReviewed" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Product"><meta itemprop="name" content="AAW in-ear monitors"></span>
        <div class="aaw-voice-card__meta" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Rating"><meta itemprop="worstRating" content="1"><meta itemprop="bestRating" content="5"><meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5"><b>5 / 5</b></div>
        <blockquote itemprop="reviewBody">Excellent sound quality and the moulding fit well to your ear. Design and craving are well make and crave.</blockquote>
        <footer itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name">Yansen T.</span></footer>
      </article>

      <article class="aaw-voice-card" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Review"><span itemprop="itemReviewed" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Product"><meta itemprop="name" content="AAW in-ear monitors"></span>
        <div class="aaw-voice-card__meta" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Rating"><meta itemprop="worstRating" content="1"><meta itemprop="bestRating" content="5"><meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5"><b>5 / 5</b></div>
        <blockquote itemprop="reviewBody">I think this IEM is very natural sound compare with previous AAW monitors CIEM which I have and improve correctly.</blockquote>
